high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the left counter with the kitchen items.
Pick up the knife on the right side next to the tomato.
Turn right, walk up and then turn left to face the kitchen counter.
Slice the cabbage that's in front of the toaster.
Turn around and walk up to the fridge.
Open the fridge door and place the knife inside. Close the door.
Return back to the sliced cabbage near the toaster.
Pick up the middle slice of the cabbage.
Turn around and head towards the other end of the kitchen.
Put the slice of cabbage in the sink next to the fork, turn on the faucet to wash, turn the faucet off.
Pick up the cabbage and go towards the fridge.
Open the fridge door, place cabbage slice next to knife, close door.
anns.task_desc: Place the sliced cabbage into the fridge.

high_descs: Turn right then face the counter by the fridge to your left.
Pick up the knife from the counter in front of you.
Turn around and face the counter on your left with the lettuce on it.
Slice the lettuce on the counter in front of you.
Turn around and face the fridge on your right.
Open the fridge, place the knife inside and close the fridge.
Turn right and face the counter with the lettuce on top of it in front of you.
Take a lettuce slice off the counter in front of you.
Turn around and head towards the counter by the sink in front of you.
Wash the lettuce in the sink in front of you and take it out.
Turn around and face the fridge to your left.
Open the fridge, place the lettuce inside and close the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Place clean lettuce in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn to your right, move forward and turn to your left and stand in front of the brown counter with a tomato
Pick up the knife from the counter
Turn to your right, move forward and turn to your left in front of the counter with a toaster.
Slice the cabbage on the edge of the counter.
Turn to your left, move forward to the refrigerator, turn to your right in front of the refrigerator
Open the refrigerator and place the knife on the tray with a brown cup on the left.
Close the refrigerator and go back to the counter with the sliced cabbage.
Pick up a slice of the cabbage from the middle
Turn to your left, move forward past the refrigerator to the sink at the end
Put the slice in the sink and run the water
Pick up the cabbage slice and go back to the refrigerator
Open the refrigerator and put the slice on the tray with the knife
anns.task_desc: Cut a cabbage, clean a slice and place it in the refrigerator

high_descs: Take a step to the right to face the counter to the right of the fridge.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn to the right and walk forward to face the lettuce on the counter.
Cut the lettuce on the counter into slices.
Turn left and walk forward to face the fridge.
Place the knife on the bottom shelf of the fridge.
Turn right and walk forward to face the lettuce on the counter.
Pick up a slice of lettuce from on the counter.
Turn left and walk around the room to face the sink.
Wash the lettuce slice in the sink and pick it back up.
Turn right and walk around to face the fridge.
Place the lettuce slice on the bottom shelf in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Cut cut lettuce into slices plus washing a slice as well as storing it in the fridge.

high_descs: Go to the counter to the right of the refrigerator.
Pick up the butter knife next to the tomato.
Turn around, walk to the counter, turn to the right, walk to the counter.
Slice the lettuce on the counter.
Turn around, walk to the refrigerator.
Put the butter knife next to the bowl in the refrigerator.
Turn around, walk to the counter, turn to the left, walk to the counter.
Pick up a slice of lettuce.
Turn around, walk to the sink.
Wash the lettuce in the sink.
Take the lettuce to the refrigerator.
Put the lettuce in the refrigerator next to the butter knife.
anns.task_desc: Place a slice of lettuce in the refrigerator with a butter knife.
